Bash Script designed to turn RPI into Router.  
Supports multiple internal NICS through bridge interface and single WAN NIC

Resizes SD Card
Sets Time
Installs needed packages and utils
Uses http://www.fars-robotics.net script to install wifi drivers
Installs and configures hostapd
Installs and configures dhcp server
Installs Fail2Ban
Firewall config (hardening WAN NIC)
Enables changing SSH Port

